OL,3,CWhy this pub landlord gets the Freedom
OL,4,Cof Derby honour
OL,6,FITV News Central Correspondent Phil
OL,7,FBrewster speaking to pub landlord,
OL,8,FSteve Kirk.
OL,10,FA well-known city centre pub landlord
OL,11,Fwill receive the prestigious Freedom
OL,12,Fof Derby honour.
OL,14,FSteve Kirk, who has run The Neptune
OL,15,Fpub in Derby for 27 years, will be
OL,16,Fgiven the special civic honour due to
OL,17,Fhis 'exceptional' fundraising efforts
OL,18,Fover many years, which have seen him
OL,19,Fraise more than #120,000 for charities.
