OL,3,CWhy this pub landlord gets the Freedom
OL,4,Cof Derby honour
OL,6,FMr Kirk, 65, will join the likes of
OL,7,Flegendary Derby boss Brian Clough,
OL,8,FOlympic gold medallist swimmer Adam
OL,9,FPeaty, Derby County FA Cup winning
OL,10,Fstar Reg Harrison and most recently
OL,11,Ffemale boxing world champion Sandy
OL,12,FRyan to be awarded the Freedom of
OL,13,FDerby.
OL,15,FCouncillor Ingall, who serves
OL,16,FChellaston and Shelton Lock, said Mr
OL,17,FKirk has raised more than #120,000 for
OL,18,Fthe Royal British Legion with loyal
OL,19,Fcommitment to support the national
OL,20,Fpoppy appeal over many years.
