OL,3,CWhy this pub landlord gets the Freedom
OL,4,Cof Derby honour
OL,6,F"In 2023 alone, he collected #17.6k.
OL,7,FOver the course of 15 years, Mr Kirk
OL,8,Fhas coordinated charitable events and
OL,9,Finitiatives involving hundreds of
OL,10,Fvolunteers and including several
OL,11,Fimpressive feats of endurance.
OL,13,F"Notable achievements include rowing
OL,14,F15 miles between Shardlow and
OL,15,FWillington, as well as walking a
OL,16,Fdistance equivalent of Derby to
OL,17,FGlasgow in just one month.
