OL,3,CWhy this pub landlord gets the Freedom
OL,4,Cof Derby honour
OL,6,F"During his 27 years behind the bar at
OL,7,Fthe Neptune, the pub has become
OL,8,Fclosely associated with Derby County
OL,9,Fand renowned for its friendly
OL,10,Fatmosphere, particularly on Christmas
OL,11,FDay when it stays open to serve hot
OL,12,Fmeals.
OL,14,F"Moreover, Steve has dedicated his
OL,15,Ftime to many other causes and
OL,16,Finitiatives, including volunteering
OL,17,Ffor the NHS at the Derby Arena, when
OL,18,Fit was used a vaccination centre
OL,19,Fduring the Covid-19 pandemic.
