OL,3,CWhy this pub landlord gets the Freedom
OL,4,Cof Derby honour
OL,6,F"Council commends Steve Kirk for his
OL,7,Fdedication and commitment to his
OL,8,Fchosen charities, as well as for the
OL,9,Frole he has played at the heart of
OL,10,FDerby's community over many years.
OL,12,F"Council resolves to request that the
OL,13,Fmayor convene an extraordinary meeting
OL,14,Ffor the matter to be determined."
